                <note><hi rend="italic">Top of letter</hi>: ‘I have often marvelled at change *of growth of flowers &amp; creepers [<hi rend="italic">interl</hi>] in Ivy—but I had no idea that the change <hi rend="italic">[</hi>was<hi rend="italic">]</hi> so permanent as you show— I am particularly surprised to hear of change of roots. There is a tropical root climber (I forget name) which changes almost in same way as ivy | How many subjects you have attended to’<ref target="#foot.f5"/> <hi rend="italic">pencil</hi></note>
